text: Dhurnal is a village and Union Council, an administrative subdivision, of Chakwal District in the Punjab Province of Pakistan. It is part of Talagang Tehsil and is located at 32° 48' 0"N 72° 6' 0"E.Location of Dhurnal – Falling Rain Genomics ==References== Category:Union councils of Chakwal District
